<!-- How We Work / Service Workflow Section -->
<section class="workflow-section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="hero-badge">Our Operational Process</span>
    <h2>Engineered for Precision & Speed</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">A transparent, rigorous 3-step methodology designed to eliminate unexpected failures and minimize plant downtime.</p>
    
    <div class="workflow-grid">
      
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="workflow-card">
        <div class="workflow-number">01</div>
        <div class="workflow-content">
          <h3>Rapid Diagnosis & Inspection</h3>
          <p>When an emergency breakdown occurs or preventative maintenance is scheduled, our engineers deploy advanced diagnostic tooling. We perform comprehensive mechanical teardowns, electrical insulation testing, and thermal imaging to isolate the root cause with absolute precision.</p>
          <ul class="workflow-list">
            <li>✓ On-site or workshop fault-finding</li>
            <li>✓ Insulation resistance & surge testing</li>
            <li>✓ Detailed engineering assessment report</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="workflow-card">
        <div class="workflow-number">02</div>
        <div class="workflow-content">
          <h3>Precision Overhaul & Repair</h3>
          <p>Once approved, equipment is routed to our specialized workshop bays. Whether it involves complete copper rewinding for high-capacity AC/DC motors, vacuum pressure impregnation (VPI), or critical mechanical machining, every task is executed to stringent quality standards.</p>
          <ul class="workflow-list">
            <li>✓ Specialized copper winding & balancing</li>
            <li>✓ Transformer oil processing & rewinding</li>
            <li>✓ Switchgear and substation component retrofits</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="workflow-card">
        <div class="workflow-number">03</div>
        <div class="workflow-content">
          <h3>Rigorous Testing & Recommissioning</h3>
          <p>Before any unit leaves our workshop or any field technicians sign off, it undergoes extensive full-load and safety testing. We ensure complete performance verification, calibration, and alignment so your asset can be safely recommissioned right back into production.</p>
          <ul class="workflow-list">
            <li>✓ Dynamic load & performance testing</li>
            <li>✓ Quality assurance & safety sign-off</li>
            <li>✓ Rapid dispatch & on-site installation support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

