    <div class="faq-container">
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What is your standard turnaround time for emergency motor rewinds?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We understand that unexpected plant downtime costs facilities significantly. While repair times depend on motor frame size, horsepower, and extent of damage, our 24/7 workshop pipelines are optimized for rapid-turnaround emergency overhauls. We provide estimated repair timelines immediately following our initial diagnostic assessment.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Do you offer on-site fault-finding or must equipment be brought to Krugersdorp?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We provide both. Our rapid-response field engineering teams deploy directly to industrial sites across South Africa for diagnostic testing, vibration analysis, thermal imaging, and initial fault-finding. For major mechanical overhauls, copper rewinds, and rigorous load testing, equipment is safely routed to our specialized Krugersdorp workshop facility.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Are your engineering repairs and testing protocols ISO 9001 aligned?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. All diagnostic reports, insulation treatments, high-voltage testing procedures, and mechanical overhauls are executed in strict alignment with ISO 9001 quality standards and recognized industrial safety regulations to ensure absolute reliability on site.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What regions across South Africa do your breakdown teams service?</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </summary>
