          <p>Operating from our central hub in Krugersdorp, Gauteng, our emergency breakdown and field technical teams service heavy industrial clients, mining operations, power stations, and municipal infrastructure networks nationwide across South Africa.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
